Kolade Adeyemi, Kano  An unidentified Air passenger, reportedly slumped and died at the Mallam Aminu Kano International Airport, (MAKIA). The sad incident happened on Sunday, at Kano Airport when the passenger was about boarding an Abuja bound aircraft. An eyewitness revealed that the passenger was accompanied to the airport by his friend from Jigawa state, when the unfortunate incident happened. However, the identity of passenger was yet to be ascertained at the time of filing this report.  It was learnt that the passenger was immediately rushed to the hospital where he was pronounced death. The FAAN management and the Police at airport were yet to confirm the incident, declining to comment on it when our correspondent asked. 